<div class="about-page">
  <h1>About Prairie Kicks</h1>

  <p>
    Prairie Kicks is a locally owned footwear store located in Winnipeg,
    Manitoba. The business has been operating for nine years and provides
    athletic, casual, and lifestyle footwear for customers of different ages.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Products</h2>

  <p>
    We sell running shoes, basketball shoes, casual sneakers, walking shoes,
    hiking boots, sandals, slippers, socks, shoe care products, and gift cards.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Mission</h2>

  <p>
    Our mission is to provide customers with comfortable, stylish, and
    dependable footwear from popular brands at competitive prices.
  </p>

  <h2>Who We Serve</h2>

  <p>
    Prairie Kicks serves teenagers, students, professionals, athletes, and
    families in Winnipeg, throughout Manitoba, and across Canada.
  </p>

